snippet.title: The Legend of Baboo Gameplay Trailer – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Set off on a quest to save your family from an ancient evil in the Legend of Baboo, explore, fight, and climb your way through a world inspired by Eastern folklore, all while accompanied by your chonky canine companion Baboo. https://store.steampowered.com/app/2928040/The_Legend_of_Baboo/
